00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:28.000
You can't learn by worrying about screwing up.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
You gotta man up and just do the damn thing.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:35.000
You've seen a million examples by now, so you should at least know where to start.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Look, I know tracking down Amo isn't a one-man job.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.000
So when you're ready, I'll be there.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:45.000
But before anything, go talk to Remlin.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:51.000
