00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Revenge or otherwise.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.000
But then...

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:23.000
Focusing on his revenge is all he knows how to do right now.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.000
